<body>
	<div>DIV 1: DIV is a block element- needs one line </div>
	<div>DIV 2: following after div 1- needs one line</div>
	<span>SPAN 1: inline element- since its following DIV 2(block element)- moves to next line</span>
	<div> DIV 3: following after span 1- pushed to next line(since its a block element)
		<span> SPAN 2: inside div 3- stays in the same line as DIV 2 - since span is inline element </span>

	continue content of div 3 </div> 
</body>
